Soften @cream cheese (2 blocks){16%oz} in the microwave for about a minute. Chop @green onions{4}.  Add them and two cups of @crab meat{2%cups}.  Add @sour cream{1/2%cup}, @Worchestershire sauce{1.5%tsp}, @powdered sugar{2%tbsp}, @garlic powder{1/2%tsp}, and @lemon juice{1/2%tsp}.
Mix all the ingredients and bake for ~{30%minutes} at 350 degrees.  Serve hot with chips or fried wontons or pork rinds.